{"tid":137511,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"EDGE雜誌最新一期遊戲評分 薩爾達10分 Horizon同仁王9分","createTime":"2017-02-28T00:53:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T05:38:13.000Z","uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a4072824614a55045f5c8b1708a49d37d7439300","tid":137511,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T00:53:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.neogaf.com/forum/showthread.php?t=1347513\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.neogaf.com%2Fforum%2Fshowthread.php%3Ft%3D1347513&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbp8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=c88492aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.neogaf.com/forum/showthread.php?t=1347513</a><br />\nReviews<br />\nThe Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild [10] / both Wii U and Switch versions tested<br />\nHorizon Zero Dawn [9]<br />\nNioh [9]<br />\nSniper Elite 4 [7]<br />\nTorment: Tides of Numenera [8]<br />\nAaero [7] / PC<br />\nDexed [6] / PSVR<br />\nDandy Dungeon [9] / iOS<br />\n<br />\n另附上第302期同303期最高評分遊戲<br />\nResident Evil VII [9]<br />\nThe Last Guardian [9]<br />\nYakuza 0 [8]<br />\n<br />\n薩爾達傳說荒野之息成為EDGE雜誌第19隻滿分遊戲<br />\n對上一隻係2015年Bloodborne<br />\n<br />\n根據Neogaf的網友爆料，《EDGE》給出了如下評價： <br />\n<br />\n這款擁有著悠久歷史的開放世界遊戲給出的答卷，給我們帶來了20年都未曾感受過的體驗。我們上一次踏入這樣一個廣袤且充滿著魔法氣息的土地還是在《薩爾達傳說：時之笛》里，而這一切無時無刻不在吸引著我們。無數的遊戲都曾保證能夠讓我們去到地圖上任何地方，做想要做的任何事，但卻沒有任何作品能夠做得如此水到渠成，令人無法抗拒。在過去的19年裡，《時之笛》都是這個系列歷史上最受喜愛的遊戲，可惜如今它也只能屈居第二了。"},{"pid":"c7422c86b978643da9ff2ff108adbb5c2b4d7752","tid":137511,"uid":66113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:29:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710d3d8617d5bd0030e5cd3f6ebad51d0aafc2e5","tid":137511,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:30:40.000Z","msg":"老任，不了。"},{"pid":"ac4a399c2763b31f6040ac9a921adf62785719f3","tid":137511,"uid":68321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:46:30.000Z","